        <mxCell id="leg-notes-bg" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#232F3E;strokeWidth=1;dashed=1;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;fontColor=#232F3E;shadow=1;" value="• Single AWS account; multi-VPC isolation (Hub/Shared outside IAM boundaries).&#10;• Region-locked to us-east-1 by IAM boundary statements.&#10;• Terraform state in S3 with use_lockfile (no DynamoDB).&#10;• Two-phase bootstrap: scripts/01.setup_s3-backend.sh then local apply.&#10;• Default tags on every resource: Project=personal-landing-zone, ManagedBy=terraform.&#10;• CIS Conformance Pack: deferred (S3 template URI moved by AWS) — Security Hub CIS v3.0.0 covers baseline.&#10;• Spoke → hub routes via TGW: TODO in environments/hub/main.tf (second apply pass).&#10;• Destroy: scripts/02.destroy-s3-backend.sh (also tears down S3 + GH secrets + env).&#10;• Estimated monthly cost: ~$80–120 AUD (TGW attachments + NAT dominate).&#10;• All arrows on this diagram are curved (curved=1) for organic readability." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="1100" x="2440" y="1910" as="geometry" />
